sections.heading: to 52-7-6 - Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 2003, ch. 223, § 3 repealed 52-7-1 to 52-7-6 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 1990 (2nd S.S.), ch. 2, §§ 83 to 88, relating to workers' compensation oversight committee. For provisions of former sections,seethe 2002 NMSA 1978 onNMOneSource.com.
